  <name>HMCL</name>
  <summary>Hello Minecraft Launcher</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="zh_CN">Hello Minecraft 启动器</summary>
  <developer id="net.huangyuhui">
    <name>huangyuhui</name>
  </developer>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>HMCL is a free, open-source, cross-platform Minecraft launcher
      supporting Mojang/Microsoft accounts and offline mode.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Microsoft (Xbox Live) account login</li>
      <li>Automatic installation of Forge, NeoForge, Fabric, Quilt, LiteLoader and OptiFine</li>
      <li>Modpack import/export (CurseForge, Modrinth, MultiMC, MCBBS)</li>
      <li>Multi-instance management with isolated game directories</li>
      <li>Built-in mod, modpack, resource pack and world browser</li>
      <li>Automatic JVM and JavaFX provisioning</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
